description: Redevelopment of site comprising erection of building between 5 and 9 storeys in height to provide 315 residential units and 408 sq m of community, education and/or commercial space (D1/A1,A2,A3 or B1) on Sury Basin frontage; formation of new vehicular access off Seven Kings Way to serve basement carpark; provision of public open space and associated landscaping.
